10.11.21.129,10.11.10.1 "<*>" status: <*> len: <*> time: <*>

### Solution:
```python
import re
import logging

def parse_log(log_message):
    pattern = re.compile(r'(\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+),(\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+).*status:(\d+).*len:(\d+).*time:(\d+\.\d+)')
    match = pattern.match(log_message)
    if match:
        return match.groups()
